International Maritime Law Conference ( 2 )
Jiang said that China 's maritime law has played a role in promoting ocean shipping and foreign trade , shipping relations , safeguarding the rights and interests of parties involved , and improving China 's legal system through exchanges with international partners .
CMLA President Yu Xiaosong told the opening ceremony that China 's maritime legal system has improved with the development of foreign trade and ocean shipping and that the legal system has played an important role in standardizing legal affairs in ocean shipping and other marine undertakings .
It has also provided a legal base for China 's maritime judgement and arbitration that will bring China 's international shipping and trade more into the international market .
